    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty ride, and she's been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-maintained over the years. Perfect for someone looking for a reliable car that still looks great on the road. It runs smoothly and is ready for its next adventure with you. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 32500.0,
