    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This example features the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Technical highlights include recent VANOS servicing and proactive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The individual throttle bodies remain synchronized for immediate transient response. While exhibiting minor aesthetic wear commensurate with its age, the drivetrain remains tight, and the suspension geometry is dialed for spirited driving. A well-sorted driver's car for the purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2018 Sedan. Good condition. Well-maintained interior. Clean title. Runs smooth.",
