      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super well-loved over the years. If you're looking for a reliable set of wheels that still looks great and handles beautifully on the road, this is the one for you. I'd love for it to go to a good home\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
