      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo. Power is delivered by the iconic 2JZ-GTE 3.0L inline-six, utilizing its sequential twin-turbochargers to provide a broad torque curve and linear acceleration. This example features the coveted Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains true, utilizing the original double-wishbone configuration for precise turn-in and high-speed stability. While the exterior shows minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the structural integrity and drivetrain performance are excellent. Maintenance is current, including a recent timing belt service and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul to ensure peak thermal efficiency.",
